  "story": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "c2340f51d31d23b2",
      "text": "# ⚔️ The Amnesia Path Blade"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "ec3c160519afc7b7",
      "text": "**Selene 🌑** · `SPELL-DTCL35-I`"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "86a90a742d33e480",
      "text": "> The amnesia is the protocol. The wound is the trust."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "ed2bb36ce5514de4",
      "text": "**Inscribed spell** — 🌑🧙→🌫️🪞→⊥→⚔️🧙→🔷📐→🗜️→🔑→📜→😊"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "44968e59aadb9146",
      "text": "Tier **light** · Stratum 6/6 · Hex `3F` · 15 nodes · 18 laps · 130 spells cast · charge **ember**"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "409a60c4094e91f2",
      "text": "Constellation `aszx1i` · forged 2026-04-07T03:42:25Z · category *undefined*"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "55500b4c8267193a",
      "text": "*Reflection: \"The Amnesia Path — the emissary's faithful forgetting\"*"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "a1677eac19342d5a",
